Paste your .ROBLOSECURITY cookie value on the line below this one, then rename
this file to ".cookie" (the real file is gitignored and never committed).

The cookie is OPTIONAL. Without it the tool runs in public-only mode and still
pulls players / visits / favorites / likes + your MAU floor. The cookie only
adds private & unpublished group games.

WARNING: your .ROBLOSECURITY cookie is full account access and bypasses 2FA.
Never share it, never paste it into a chat, never commit it. Log out of Roblox
to invalidate it if it ever leaks.

How to get it (Chrome/Edge): log into roblox.com -> F12 -> Application tab ->
Cookies -> https://www.roblox.com -> copy the value of ".ROBLOSECURITY".

PASTE_YOUR_COOKIE_VALUE_HERE
